<h1 id="一键三连"><a href="#一键三连" class="headerlink" title="一键三连"></a>一键三连</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean; hexo g; hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
